      "text": "SHARMA, Garima, GRECO, Angela, GREWATSCH, Sylvia and BANSAL, Pratima (Tima), 2022. Cocreating Forward: How Researchers and Managers Can Address Problems Together. Academy of Management Learning & Education. September 2022. Vol. 21, no. 3, p. 350–368. DOI 10.5465/amle.2021.0233. "
